'''pair of compasses''' (''plural'': '''pairs of compasses''')

# A [[tool]] used to draw [[circle]]s; it usually consists of two arms that are joined at one end in such a way that the arms can be opened and closed; one of the arms is pointed at its free end while the other holds a pencil, pencil lead or some other implement for making marks.

